适的基础设施让印度无法成为奥运强国。而且，印度最好的运动员大多数都从事板球运动，这也是该国最受欢迎的运动。不过，板球并不是奥运会比赛项目。 报道最后也提到，由于印度政府在体育和运动员上加大了投入，印度参加奥运会的运动员数量近年正在稳步增加。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-272f96e412cdb6f136e7b506a8b7f87d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/477512978"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5KrftJDdlJ0sEAMaCDY4Mzk0Nzk0INe8rogGMIABOJ0PQDByCTQ3NzUxMjk3OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1628309025.9206955", "card_id": "Q_292279985", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 6194}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你后悔嫁给现在的老公吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "镜像问题：你后悔娶了现在的老婆吗？ 相关问题：为什么男的大都不后悔娶了现在的老婆，而女的大都后悔嫁给现在的老公？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-374e523ce72ebb380392e37a4f0e0cd8_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/292279985"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI5KrftJDdlJ0sEAMaCDI3MjI4MTE2ILrDkdwFMEI4uM8BQDFyCTI5MjI3OTk4NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "next": "", "previous": ""}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新"}